</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d263n1-ptr" id="PJA11d263n1">1</a>

   <p>Dumas advisor has not been identified.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d263n2-ptr" id="PJA11d263n2">2</a>

   <p>Dumas refers to his translation of <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s memorial of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0204" class="document">19 April</a>, above.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d263n3-ptr" id="PJA11d263n3">3</a>

   <p>The Duc de La Vauguyon.</p>

